Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:02.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:09.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:16.11,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:22.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.93,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:28.98,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:35.51,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:44.98,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:51.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:54.48,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:02:00.83,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:06.11,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢贵方接纳本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军欧亚联盟军事要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座建于偏僻小行星上的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因有被称为阿尔狄弥斯之伞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光波防御带的庇护
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍是难攻不落的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尽千辛万苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆脱克鲁泽队追击的大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 躲入其伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校阁下？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保持安静 舰长同志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.88,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1180,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}消失的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了 什么事 赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 都别动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都集中到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米坦诺夫少校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为安保措施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁了舰船的操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和火控系统而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰既未登录船籍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无我军识别代码
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于大局考虑允许你们入港
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遗憾的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还未被视为友军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是军事设施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待不周 还请谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请士官跟我走一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那里听你们的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干什么了 给我放尊重点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大西洋联邦 机密军事计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会连滚带爬逃进我们这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫利奥波利斯介入其中的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们在这里多住一阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明舰船上三位士官带到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是放我们在这里下船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧亚联盟不是自己人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大西洋联邦关系不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键是没识别代码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题那么严重？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的问题 我看在其他方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫·拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔尔·巴基露露少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你们的ID确实隶属大西洋联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你响当当的大名我也早有耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩底弥翁之鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格尔马蒂战线上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有参战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉德准将的部队？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战局上虽然败下阵来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你击落5台Ginn的光辉战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们提振了不少士气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和那艘战舰一起出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 请恕我不能说明详情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但立即补给难度很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须分秒必争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶往月球总部基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面… 还有扎夫特军埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉西亚级？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你们所见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在伞外四处徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不厌其烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 一两艘巡洋舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这里够不成什么威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们完成补给也无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目标 是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若长期滞留 难保不会牵连阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵连？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座阿尔狄弥斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终会无功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 不妨先休息一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看你们相当疲倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让人给你们安排房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们走后 也可便于与月球总部联系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不急于一时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的这么安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就像在母亲的怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情况得到什么时候才结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他们不回来 什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能跟友军造反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乱啊 地球军里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是不明舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种待遇显然欠妥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怕我们回船上做坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最担心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为阿尔狄弥斯绝对安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞能阻挡所有激光和实弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 从里朝外也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不攻击我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够傻冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作为防御兵器数一数二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加之不是重要据点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军从未打算攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此暂时没有突破伞的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪只怪让他们逃进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到他们出来尿尿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你还笑得出 提亚哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等队长回来 你去报告说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们一无所获」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞并非时刻张开的对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 周围安全时不会启用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不论多快的突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不如伞打开得快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会白费功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的那台机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅雷也许有办法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体除相转移装甲以外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一种很有意思的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特罗拉西亚级战舰撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄色18.20C 距离700
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍在继续远离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 下面交给莱兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续加强对空戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上查得还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是机动战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OS被上了锁 到现在还没能启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在技术部全员出动正在解锁…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与阿尔狄弥斯距离达到3500
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光波防御带依然没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海市蜃楼系统 检查电磁压
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 不做实验直接上阵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 地球军还真爱造些下流兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给尼科尔用再合适不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪几个是船上的驾驶员和技师？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员和技师是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就在你们中间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来问我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为舰长他们不说是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为 你们问不出口？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把强袭的启动程序锁好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让除你以外的任何人动它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是大西洋联邦中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选来执行机密任务的优秀士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想把强袭怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 难得在面世之前一睹机体尊容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弗拉戈上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话请去问上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们监控了你们之前的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使用枪桶式零式的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了他没有别人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我比谁都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人驾驶的可能性虽然很低
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考虑到这船的舰长也是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 卑鄙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶那东西的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岗哨定时报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近距离防空圈内未发现敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起全方位光波防御带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转入二级戒备状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海市蜃楼粒子正常生成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散布减损率35%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多能用80分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄救美是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你这样的新兵蛋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能驾驶得了那东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在我面前摆谱！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有理由让你打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉说得是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁再敢胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把那种事说出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我又没说假话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉会怎么样 你没想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一口一个你啊你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是友军基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好担心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道地球军在跟谁打仗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给OS解锁就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的能力不只限于此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 解析它的构造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造相同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是制造专门对付这种机动战士的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个普通学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是军人也没有军籍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没理由要求我做这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是个调整人中的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论出于什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然背叛了同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如为我们做点事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在地球一边的调整人非常难得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必过分担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会得到很好的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在欧亚联盟中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次信里说母亲的病情加重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管制室 这震动是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不明 周边未发现敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这爆炸怎么解释？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 是攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是超射程攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开防护伞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防…防御区域内发现机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在逐次破坏发生器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在港口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这警报到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快去问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想这都是攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站…站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候你们就省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备启动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可舰长他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会变成靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 不幸言中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！墙上被炸开口子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喊啊 骗他们开门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 救命 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉没空解释
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我可不想和阿尔狄弥斯殉情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞被毁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在被攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有空做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它 今天必须死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到这种地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同要塞一起办了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要塞莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里施展不开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是个调整人里的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在地球一边的调整人非常难得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再来管我们！
