Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫回强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从背面港口离开阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号出发 最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是…
